    </tags>
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>boot-hell</title>
    <link href="/2023/10/10/boot-hell/"/>
    <url>/2023/10/10/boot-hell/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>前阵子为了保存我的硬盘，使用dd将我电脑的<code>nvme1n1</code>和<code>nvme0n1</code>全部烧了一个备份出来，<br>当我今天心血来潮把<code>ubuntu.img</code>烧到<code>window</code>的盘里面的时候，出现了boot-hell(本来想称其为os-hell,但是搞不定的原因还是对os的boot了解太浅了)</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">┌💁  z @ 💻  z <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> 📁  tabbleman.github.io<br>└❯ sudo su<br>root@z:/home/z/projects/my_git/blog/tabbleman.github.io<span class="hljs-comment"># history | grep dd</span><br>  128  <span class="hljs-built_in">dd</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>=/dev/nvme0n1p2 of=/media/z/Cheems/ubuntu.iso status=progress<br>  131  <span class="hljs-built_in">dd</span> bs=40960 <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>=/dev/nvme0n1 of=/media/z/Cheems/ubuntu.iso status=progress<br>  133  <span class="hljs-built_in">dd</span> bs=32M <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>=/dev/nvme0n1 of=/media/z/Cheems/ubuntu.img status=progress<br>  138  <span class="hljs-built_in">dd</span> bs=32M <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>=/dev/nvme1n1 of=/media/z/Cheems/window.iso status=progress<br>  141  <span class="hljs-built_in">dd</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>=window.iso of=/dev/nvme1n1 bs=32M status=progress<br>  142  <span class="hljs-built_in">dd</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>=ubuntu.iso of=/dev/nvme1n1 bs=32M status=progress<br>  144  <span class="hljs-built_in">dd</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>=ubuntu.img of=/dev/nvme1n1 bs=32M status=progress<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>update:<br>2023-10-10-16:47完成将<code>window.img</code>重新烧回原来window，希望能好。。。<br>update:<br>2023-10-10-19:24成功恢复window，应该是<code>window boot manager</code>发现了原来是window的地方变成了ubuntu导致引导失败。准备在别的电脑再试试</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
    <tags>
      
      <tag>trivia</tag>
      
    </tags>
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>github-page-setup</title>
    <link href="/2023/10/10/github-page-setup/"/>
    <url>/2023/10/10/github-page-setup/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="prerequest"><a href="#prerequest" class="headerlink" title="prerequest"></a>prerequest</h1><p>一个github账号<br>nodejs &gt;&#x3D; 14 </p><h1 id="start"><a href="#start" class="headerlink" title="start"></a>start</h1><h2 id="1-建立一个github仓库"><a href="#1-建立一个github仓库" class="headerlink" title="1.建立一个github仓库"></a>1.建立一个github仓库</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/new">建立仓库</a><br>建议仓库命名为<code>&lt;username&gt;.github.io (e.g.) tabbleman.github.io</code><br>然后把这个url复制下来</p><h2 id="2-下载hexo-cli"><a href="#2-下载hexo-cli" class="headerlink" title="2.下载hexo-cli"></a>2.下载hexo-cli</h2><p>前提是已经装好了nodejs, 可以通过<code>node --version</code> 或者 <code>npm --version</code>查看<br><code>npm install hexo-cli -g </code><br>如果安装没问题那么就可以通过<code>hexo -v</code> 查看hexo安装是否没问题。</p><h2 id="3-建立写blog的文件夹"><a href="#3-建立写blog的文件夹" class="headerlink" title="3.建立写blog的文件夹"></a>3.建立写blog的文件夹</h2><p><code>hexo init blog</code>用hexo初始化blog文件夹<br>然后进入文件夹blog, 输入 <code>npm install</code> </p><p>根据<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-tw/docs/configuration">这篇blog</a>, 需要更改<code>_config.yml</code>文件<br>以下是一些需要更改的地方</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment">#第105行</span><br>deploy:<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">type</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;git&#x27;</span><br>  repo: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;项目url地址&#x27;</span><br>  branch: main <br>  message: <span class="hljs-string">&quot;update blog&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后输入<code>hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo -d</code>就好了</p><p>接下来输入<code>hexo s</code>就可以在本地<code>http://localhost:4000/</code>看到已经部署的blog</p><h2 id="撰写blog"><a href="#撰写blog" class="headerlink" title="撰写blog"></a>撰写blog</h2><p><code>hexo new page-name</code>就能建立一个新的blog了。(page-name)是要写的blog的名字<br>然后编辑<code>source/_posts/page-name.md</code>就能书写blog了<br>建议将一下内容添加成一个sh脚本</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-meta">#! /usr/bin/bash </span><br>hexo clean <br>hexo g <br>hexo d <br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> [ $? -eq 0 ]; <span class="hljs-keyword">then</span><br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Deploy completed successfully.&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span><br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Deploy failed.&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">fi</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
